![][image1]  


| sameAs | [schema.org/AlignmentObject](http://schema.org/AlignmentObject) |
| :---- | :---- |
| **definition** | An intangible item that describes an alignment between a learning resource and a node in an educational framework.  |

| Property | Description | Type | Include | Cardinality | Source |
| :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- |
| identifier | The identifier of the item, either as textual strings or as URL (URI) links.  | [Text](https://schema.org/Text) or [URL](https://schema.org/url) | MUST | 1 | Schema.org |
| alignmentType | A category of alignment between the learning resource and the framework node. Recommended values include: 'requires', ‘teaches’, 'assesses’. | [Text](https://schema.org/Text) | MUST | 1..n | Schema.org |
| educationalFramework | The framework to which the resource being described is aligned. | [Text](https://schema.org/Text) | MUST | 1 | Schema.org |
| targetDescription | The description of a node in an established educational framework. | [Text](https://schema.org/Text) | MUST | 1 | Schema.org |
| targetName | The name of a node in an established educational framework. | [Text](https://schema.org/Text) | MUST | 1 | Schema.org |
| targetUrl | The URL of a node in an established educational framework. | [URL](https://schema.org/url) | MUST | 1 | Schema.org |

---

## Usage notes

### — Alignment Type

We restrict the possible values for `alignmentType` to:

* `teaches`: the learning resource is designed to teach the referenced competency

* `assesses`: the learning resource is designed to assess the referenced competency

* `requires:`  the learning resource requires the learner to have mastered the referenced competency prior to engaging with the learning resource

---

## Example

```javascript
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "AlignmentObject",
  "alignmentType": "teaches",
  "educationalFramework": "Common Core State Standards for Math",
  "targetDescription": "Represent data with plots on the real number line (dot plots, histograms, and box plots).",
  "targetName": "HSS-ID.A.1",
  "targetUrl": "https://satchelcommons.com/ims/case/v1p0/CFItems/6b9c8faf-d7cc-11e8-824f-0242ac160002", 
}
```
